E: paul@easytaxi.com  www.easytaxi.comDesired Skills and ExperienceDesired skills and experience are:   ◦                    Min 2-4 years of experience, preferably in agency environment ◦                    Experience in campaign management on Facebook, Google, Bing, Twitter, or affiliate networks ◦                    Experience with offline marketing – events, promotions, vouchers, etc. ◦                    Ideally with relevant certification – Google AdWords, Bing, Hubspot, WOMMA, or others ◦                    Proficient in smartphone usage, in particular mobile applications ◦                    Ability to get things done independently outside of the office, or in a team ◦                    Analytical skills and love for numbers are a MUST ◦                    Ability to come up with creative solutions ◦                    Fluent in spoken and written English (offical office language at Easy Taxi) and minimum one local language. You will be based in Singapore but the role includes a possibility to travel when needed.About this companyEasy TaxiWe are Easy Taxi Easy Taxi is the biggest taxi hailing mobile app in the World with operations in 30+ countries, including Brazil, Argentina, Mexico, Malaysia, Singapore, Thailand, Taiwan, Hong Kong, and Egypt! Easy Taxi was launched in September 2012 and aims to change the taxi market around the world by offering passenger a fast, convenient and safe way of booking taxis, while increasing the safety of taxi drivers and, especially, their revenues.   Due to our rapid expansion we are now looking for marketing campaign manager to help with the regional execution of our marketing efforts, both on offline and online platforms.Similar jobsSingaporePosted 14 hours agoSingaporePosted 6 days agoSingaporePosted 15 days agoSingaporePosted 22 hours agoSingaporePosted 15 days agoSingaporePosted 29 days agoSingaporePosted 19 days agoSingaporePosted 15 days agoSingaporePosted 4 days agoSingaporePosted 22 days agoThis is a preview of th